change.subject: Adds serial consumer-producer scenario
change.commitMessage:
Adds serial consumer-producer scenario

This scenario benchmarks a serial consumer-producer
use case: creates a queue, sends messages to it,
retrieves messages from it and deletes the queue.

Some changes have been added to the fakes to test this
scenario properly.

Change-Id: I49d5956bbf571840829b3e9b1411a907748cf1ed
